assignedVehicleRole 
Behavior: local 
Game: Armed Assault (1.05) 
Description: Return the role a unit is assigned to within its assigned vehicle 
. 
The array which is returned contains: [] - Not assigned to any vehicle 
 ["Driver"] - Assigned as driver ["Cargo"] - Assigned as cargo ["Turret 
", [turret path]] - Assigned to a turret 
If no vehicle role is assigned, an empty array is returned. 
 
 
Syntax:  
 Array = assignedVehicleRole unitName 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
Return Value: 
 Array